Text: Helmer2, the second part of that story is how confused the sheep were after he shaved.  His favorite ewe didn't know him either.
Religion aside, it is a funny joke. It was even funnier when Helmer2's aunt told it to me about his mother...
and kalusa would know... he is such a baaaahd boy... but it was the only action he could get...
and no, i am not a muslim. but i don't suffer fools gladly. besides, now you get a taste of your own medicine....
